title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 4-10.9 - Breakable gages
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 4-10.9 - Breakable gages

State Regulations
A glass gage or sight feed, the breakage of which will
allow the discharge of fuel oil from the fuel supply system, shall not be
used. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12

4-10.9

comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
